Writing pseudocode for doing laundry:

Gather the clothes to wash.
Store the clothes in a laundry basket.
Open the washing machine door.
Place the clothes into the washing machine.
Adjust the water level on the washing machine.
Measure the laundry detergent.
Place the laundry detergent in the washing machine.
Close the washing machine door.
Waiting for its completion.
Open the dryer door after washing has been completed.
Move the clothes from the washing machine to the dryer.
Close the dryer door.
Switch the dryer from the "Off" position to the "On" position.
Waiting for its completion.
Remove the clothes once they have finished drying.
